                <Header>Name that Grape</Header>
                <Paragraph>Using a grape variety name on an American wine label is optional. Nevertheless, many wineries and bottlers show this information on their labels. The TTB designed its "Grape Variety Designations on American Wine Labels" web page to help explain the rules.</Paragraph>
            </EntitySourceOfInformation>
