                </FooterDetails>
                <Header/>
                <Paragraph>The TTB Administrator has approved a list of grape variety names for use as American wine type designations. This list has been assigned to "Subpart J—American Grape Variety Names" of part 4 in 27 CFR.</Paragraph>
            </EntitySourceOfInformation>
